It absorbs into the skin within seconds, leaving a glossy, smooth finish on the face. It fades dark spots and helps control acne, making it an excellent product,particularly for oily and combination skin types.

✨ Glowing Skin Routine for Combination Skin! ✨
This 5-step skincare routine is perfect if you struggle with oily T-zones and dry cheeks. These products balance hydration, remove excess oil, and boost radiance 🌿💛

🌸 Step 1: Gentle Cleanser – Dot & Key Mango Face Wash
➡️ Keywords: gentle face wash, mango cleanser, face wash for oily skin
This fruity cleanser lifts away dirt & oil while keeping your skin soft and supple – perfect for combo skin types!

💧 Step 2: Soothing Toner – Cetaphil Toner
➡️ Keywords: alcohol-free toner, toner for sensitive skin, calming toner
A mild and hydrating toner that helps soothe inflammation and prep your skin for layering.

🫐 Step 3: Lightweight Moisturizer – Dot & Key Blueberry Moisturizer
➡️ Keywords: blueberry moisturizer, lightweight moisturizer for combo skin, antioxidant moisturizer
It hydrates without clogging pores, reduces dullness, and smells amazing!

☀️ Step 4: Hydrating Sunscreen – Aqualogica Sunscreen
➡️ Keywords: sunscreen for combination skin, SPF for oily skin, non-greasy sunscreen
Lightweight, water-based, and leaves NO white cast. It protects while adding hydration.

👁 Step 5: Brightening Eye Cream – Dot & Key Eye Cream
➡️ Keywords: under-eye cream, puffiness reducer, eye cream for dark circles
Reduces puffiness, fine lines, and dark circles—waking up your eyes instantly!

✨ Pro Tip: Stick with this routine consistently to see visible glow, clear skin, and improved texture. Morning or night—this works wonders! 💫
